ch.bfh.ti.gravis.core.graph

Interface IGravisGraph

  • All Superinterfaces:
    edu.uci.ics.jung.graph.Graph<IVertex,IEdge>, edu.uci.ics.jung.graph.Hypergraph<IVertex,IEdge>
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    IEditGraphObservable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    EditGraphDecorator, GravisGraph

    public interface IGravisGraph
extends edu.uci.ics.jung.graph.Graph<IVertex,IEdge>
    This interface extends the JUNG Graph interface and adds some additional methods. The edgeType is either directed or undirected for all edges (depends on the edge type of this graph). Parallel edges and hyper-edges are not allowed. All vertices and edges in this graph must have a unique name. Only one start and one end vertex is allowed.
    Author:
    Patrick Kofmel (kofmp1@bfh.ch)
